{"tid":1794570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[賣國]央視引述文在寅指香港事務及新疆問題都是中國內政","createTime":"2019-12-23T08:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T16:03:26.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f7d463d5e1da6cc26f7983d995e40eea1b93380c","tid":1794570,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:13:54.000Z","msg":"內地央視報道，訪華的南韓總統文在寅，提及香港及新疆。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，文在寅祝賀中華人民共和國成立70周年，又說韓方認為無論香港事務，抑或涉及新疆問題，都是中國內政。文在寅又說，韓方理解中方在重大問題上的立場，支持自由貿易，願意與中方繼續加強在地區與國際事務中的溝通協作。<br />\n<br />\n文在寅早前在北京，與國家主席習近平，舉行雙邊會面，稍後轉往成都，出席明日舉行的中日韓領導人會議。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499192-20191223.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499192-20191223.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwc2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=493e5a85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499192-20191223.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=82e0acc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499192-20191223.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"0eb8a1dbf3f3aa28ac1ecfed34559e72b0e3ad28","tid":1794570,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:22:13.000Z","msg":"好在香港人打既海外戰線不限於政府層面"},{"pid":"3d94af4f891c9ba6b0c95bb9415bc753d167ce0b","tid":1794570,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:20:38.000Z","msg":"垃圾總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3d4afbf9840c86382afac8fd1069a87929f300","tid":1794570,"uid":315761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:22:40.000Z","msg":"支那人民共和國南朝鮮特別行政區<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96522f5f3a86e88764a13c